text: Food is genuinely nice. I had nasi lemak deluxe set that come with a drink. Right now there is opening promo with 20% discount. Do support this humble eatery that staff serve with a big heart!
My favorite local cafe now has a branch in Tai Seng! Another location for me to enjoy my Kopi O and Curry Chicken, and Nasi Lemak + Thai Milk Tea for my boy üëçüòÑ
